---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Investor Relations | Lupine">
  <main class="reference-container">
    <header class="formal-header">
      <div class="seal">CONFIDENTIAL // PERFORMANCE METRICS</div>
      <h1>Institutional Validation Manuscript</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Empirical validation metrics establishing the Atlas Distill technological moat</p>
    </header>

    <section class="reading-layout">
      <div class="marginalia">
        <span class="citation-note"><strong>The Technological Moat:</strong> By automating the ingestion of NIST parameterizations, Lupine achieves a 10,000x acceleration in validation throughput compared to manual phenomenological fitting.</span>
        <span class="citation-note"><strong>Validation Protocol:</strong> All metrics shown are cross-validated using density functional theory (DFT) baseline references.</span>
      </div>
      <article class="manuscript">
        <h2>1. Atlas Engine Capabilities</h2>
        <p>The Atlas Distill engine represents a definitive leap in materials informatics. By converting the legacy empirical physics ecosystem into a unified, programmable data structure, we enable high-frequency algorithmic discovery of novel material properties.</p>
        
        <div class="validation-table-container">
          <h2>2. System Accuracy Benchmarks</h2>
          <p class="summary-text">Crystalline Stability Metrics (NIST-884 Compliance). Utilizing <em>Space Grotesk</em> tabular figures for exact precision.</p>
          <table class="validation-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>PARAMETER (Silicon)</th>
                <th>DFT REFERENCE</th>
                <th>ATLAS OBSERVED</th>
                <th>DELTA (Δ)</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Lattice Constant (a)</td>
                <td class="data">5.4309 Å</td>
                <td class="data">5.4312 Å</td>
                <td class="data highlight-good">+0.0003</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Cohesive Energy</td>
                <td class="data">-4.63 eV/atom</td>
                <td class="data">-4.61 eV/atom</td>
                <td class="data highlight-warn">+0.02</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Bulk Modulus (B)</td>
                <td class="data">97.6 GPa</td>
                <td class="data">97.8 GPa</td>
                <td class="data highlight-good">+0.2</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>C11 Elastic Constant</td>
                <td class="data">165.8 GPa</td>
                <td class="data">166.1 GPa</td>
                <td class="data highlight-warn">+0.3</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Isotropic Strain Limit</td>
                <td class="data">0.0012</td>
                <td class="data">0.0014</td>
                <td class="data highlight-warn">+0.0002</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">The table above demonstrates our ability to constrain predictions within extraordinarily tight tolerances. This level of empirical certainty is what defines our computational sovereignty strategy.</p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .reference-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .formal-header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .seal {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .formal-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .reading-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .marginalia {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    position: sticky;
    top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .citation-note {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--primary-container);
    padding-left: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .manuscript h2 {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .manuscript p {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  .validation-table-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .validation-table-container h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .summary-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif !important;
    font-size: 1rem !important;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant) !important;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl) !important;
    max-width: 100% !important;
  }

  .validation-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .validation-table th {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .validation-table td {
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--on-surface);
  }

  .validation-table td.data {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .highlight-good {
    color: var(--secondary);
  }
  
  .highlight-warn {
    color: var(--tertiary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .reading-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .marginalia {
      position: static;
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
      padding-top: var(--space-md);
      margin-top: var(--space-md);
    }
    .validation-table {
      display: block;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
